<item>
            <title>[LU-7223] Failover - mmp: MMP was not enabled on /dev/lvm-Role_OSS/P1 on ost1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7223</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No subtests ran. suite-log shows following issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;modules unloaded.
excepting tests: 
CMD: onyx-42vm3 dumpe2fs -h /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 | grep mmp
onyx-42vm3: dumpe2fs 1.42.13.wc3 (28-Aug-2015)
Filesystem features:      has_journal ext_attr resize_inode dir_index filetype mmp flex_bg dirdata sparse_super large_file huge_file uninit_bg dir_nlink quota
CMD: onyx-42vm4 dumpe2fs -h /dev/lvm-Role_OSS/P1 | grep mmp
onyx-42vm4: dumpe2fs 1.42.13.wc3 (28-Aug-2015)
 mmp : @@@@@@ FAIL: MMP was not enabled on /dev/lvm-Role_OSS/P1 on ost1 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/bc9071ca-632c-11e5-afa7-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/bc9071ca-632c-11e5-afa7-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
